name: Season 2 Epilogue 001: LARK
description:
Born and raised in the Vessels colony, Lark has always known this place as her home. She doesn't come from high society and she has a knack for getting out of scrapes or for being in the right place at the right time. Lucky, you might call it. Drawn to Dutch's casino - the promise of wealth and power - Lark will see just how far her Luck will carry her. If she can control it.

This piece was made as a prize for Valkyr for his amazing Fan Fiction entry for the Dutch’s Casino prompt.
